Enchanted Bricks & Bewitching Brews: A Harry Potter Lego Night!
Wednesday, July 23, 2025
5:00‚ÄØPM
10:00‚ÄØPM
Google Calendar
ICS
Calling all witches, wizards, and muggles!
Get ready to immerse yourself in the magical world of Harry Potter at The Argonaut Bar and Lounge's "Enchanted Bricks & Bewitching Brews" event! We've partnered with a Bricks and Minifigs of Mount Dora to bring you a truly unique and enchanting evening of creative building and delightful drinks.
Your ticket unlocks a magical experience:
Your very own LEGO Harry Potter Owl building kit
!
One complimentary drink
of your choice (draft beer, bottled beer, glass of wine, or a specially crafted Harry Potter-themed cocktail).
Throughout the evening, we'll be playing
"Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone"
on our screens, setting the perfect atmosphere for a journey to Hogwarts. Whether you're a seasoned Lego master or just looking for a fun and relaxing night out, this is the perfect opportunity to unleash your inner builder and enjoy some fantastic sips.
Must pre-purchase tickets to secure your spot and your magical Lego kit!
Space is limited, so grab your tickets before they vanish!
Purchase Tickets
